{"tid":1839843,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"這A片當年票房大收60億美元 女主卻只得1250元......《深喉》你有沒有看過？","createTime":"2020-01-24T15:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T21:01:44.000Z","uid":250639,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c7739ec93cd05f9eb6b3daaeb9fdd8404543c5","tid":1839843,"uid":250639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QkCrC2r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkCrC2r.jpg&h=7c0cb7e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天為大家帶來的是一部根據真人故事改編的電影<br />\n女主角琳達偶然一次遇上中年大叔查克<br />\n卻被深深的吸引住<br />\n給教會了「深喉」絕技<br />\n一次A片試鏡憑絕技當然成功採用<br />\n並搬上大銀幕 電影直接炮紅<br />\n票房63總共60億美元 但女主卻只收得1250美元<br />\n銀幕背後隱藏住琳達17天地獄般的夢魘<br />\n<br />\n這A片當年票房大收60億美元 女主卻只得1250元......《深喉》你有沒有看過？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x28_ed6_vsU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx28_ed6_vsU&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77dUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=2a5c232e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x28_ed6_vsU</a>"},{"pid":"8523ba901335776dd46a23cb3ce99660c5b0675c","tid":1839843,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:38:31.000Z","msg":"Estimates of the film's total revenues have varied widely: numbers as high as $600 million (equivalent to $3.7 billion today) have been cited, which would make Deep Throat one of the highest-grossing films of all time. With an average ticket price of $5 ($30.56 today), box-office takings of $600 million would imply 120 million admissions, an unrealistic figure.[2] Although subsequent sales of the film on home video certainly brought additional revenue, the FBI's estimate that the film produced an income of approximately $100 million ($611 million today) may be closer to the truth. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係6億，唔係60億<br />\n而且只係推測<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deep_Throat_(film)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FDeep_Throat_%28film%29&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77dUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=dc37888f\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deep_Throat_(film)</a>"},{"pid":"8c662e082f27fe8d63bad8e49f47dfff04461c77","tid":1839843,"uid":62532,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/e/e6/PCixu.gif/revision/latest?cb=20110801124142\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fe%2Fe6%2FPCixu.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20110801124142&h=d495e646&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b2ed4d31cbb04deaac5ecabbf98ad8a3c25a164","tid":1839843,"uid":103230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"endgame 全球都係30億<br />\n你計通脹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0aadd29486ca08abf4ca8548722c2b613c6b02a","tid":1839843,"uid":250639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8523ba901335776dd46a23cb3ce99660c5b0675c","tid":1839843,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T15:38:31.000Z","msg":"Estimates of the film's total revenues have varied widely: numbers as high as $600 million (equivalent to $3.7 billion today) have been cited, which would make Deep Throat one of the highest-grossing films of all time. With an average ticket price of $5 ($30.56 today), box-office takings of $600 million would imply 120 million admissions, an unrealistic figure.[2] Although subsequent sales of the film on home video certainly brought additional revenue, the FBI's estimate that the film produced an income of approximately $100 million ($611 million today) may be closer to the truth. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係6億，唔係60億<br />\n而且只係推測<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deep_Throat_(film)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FDeep_Throa